        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Hoodies That Redefine Comfort</strong></h3><p>First up, let\u2019s talk hoodies. The Bogey Boys Essentials Hoodies are all about balancing laid-back style with functionality. Constructed with soft, breathable fabrics that keep you cosy without overheating, these hoodies come in dynamic colours like <strong>Bogey Blue</strong> and <strong>Midnight</strong>, making them perfect for those cooler mornings on the green.</p><ul><li><strong>Key Features</strong>:</li><li><em>Material</em>: Blended fabrics for ultimate comfort and breathability</li><li><em>Fit</em>: Tailored for flexibility during your swing, ensuring maximum movement</li><li><em>Colours</em>: Available in bold colours like Bogey Blue and classic neutrals like Midnight and Black</li></ul><p>Pair these hoodies with your favourite golf trousers or even denim for a casual outing after your round. Whether you\u2019re preparing for an early tee time or lounging post-game, these hoodies offer versatility that easily transitions from sporty to streetwear.</p>"
          }
        }
