        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Polos Built for Performance</strong></h3><p>Of course, no golf collection is complete without polos, and the Bogey Boys Essentials Polos are a standout. Crafted with a mix of cotton and polyester for moisture-wicking performance, these polos will keep you feeling fresh all day long. The <em>Athletic Polos</em> come in eye-catching hues like <strong>Bogey Blue</strong> and <strong>Eden Green</strong>, ideal for those looking to make a statement while staying cool under pressure.</p><ul><li><strong>Key Features</strong>:</li><li><em>Moisture-wicking technology</em>: Keeps you dry, even on the hottest days</li><li><em>Stretch fabric</em>: Provides the flexibility needed for an unrestricted swing</li><li><em>Design</em>: Vibrant yet sophisticated, perfect for both casual and tournament play</li></ul><p>When you\u2019re looking for that blend of tradition and modern athleticism, these polos should be at the top of your list. The structure and stretch make them a staple for your golf wardrobe, offering functionality without sacrificing style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
