          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>Script Golf Towels: Where Function Meets Fashion</strong></h2><p>What\u2019s a round of golf without the proper accessories? The <strong>Script Golf Towels</strong> from Bogey Boys are more than just an afterthought \u2013 they\u2019re a statement piece. Made from high-quality materials with excellent absorbency, these towels are perfect for wiping down your clubs, hands, or even your face between swings.</p><p>The bold <strong>Bogey Boys script logo</strong> adds a touch of flair, making these towels the perfect blend of fashion and function. Not only do they perform well, but they also look great hanging from your golf bag.</p><ul><li><strong>Key Features</strong>:</li><li><em>Premium absorbent fabric</em>: Ensures effective moisture control</li><li><em>Logo design</em>: Bold script for a standout look</li><li><em>Practical size</em>: Large enough for utility, but not bulky</li></ul><p>Whether you\u2019re an avid golfer or just appreciate quality accessories, these towels are an essential addition to your gear.</p>"
          }
        }
