          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>The BB Range: Golf Apparel with a Retro Flair</strong></h2><p>For those who love to merge performance with style, the <strong>BB Range</strong> from Bogey Boys is the answer. This collection pulls from vintage aesthetics, with designs that echo the 70s and 80s, all while ensuring you stay on top of your game. The range includes everything from retro-inspired polos to stylish outerwear and pants, giving you the confidence to stand out whether you\u2019re on the green or at a social event post-game.</p><ul><li><strong>Key Features</strong>:</li><li><em>Vintage-inspired</em>: Perfect for golfers who love a unique, throwback look</li><li><em>Comprehensive collection</em>: Offers everything from polos and pants to outerwear</li><li><em>Performance-focused</em>: Designed to meet the needs of the modern golfer</li></ul><p>Golfers with a keen sense of fashion will love the BB Range. Not only do the pieces perform well, but they also bring a nostalgic twist to your golf wardrobe.</p>"
          }
